<h1>About the Debian Installer</h1>

<p>
The Debian-Installer is the replacement for the aging "boot-floppies"
installation system used in all previous versions of debian. The Debian
Installer will be the installer for future versions of Debian, beginning
with sarge. It has been designed to be more modular, easier to use, and
more extensible than the old installation system.
</p>

